data.description: Welcome Home to the sought after community of Sunshine Village!  This open floorplan welcomes you when you walk through the front door! The kitchen features beautiful dark wood cabinets and plenty of counter space with room for seating at the island!  Kitchen opens up to the dining room/living room area which is perfect for entertaining!  Master bedroom features an en-suite bathroom with double sinks and tub with shower.  Nicely sized walk in closet as well!  Remaining 3 bedrooms are nicely sized...perfect to host overnight guests!  Sliders open up to a nice fenced in back yard!  Close to an array of restaraunts and shopping!  Don't miss out on this one...it won't last long!
